Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.96,0:00:00.00,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.87,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:I don't wanna let the chance slip away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:59.08,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Why is my freedom taken away?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.91,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  reason as against emotion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:06.65,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  l've gotta deal with extreme frustration
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:10.08,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:All my efforts will never be in vain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:13.04,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Endless desire,like a haunting refrain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:16.44,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:Such a pain,the ideal versus the real
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.90,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:There is a way E:To change the world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:20.42,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:Just count on me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.77,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:So what if I sing off-key,who cares
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.85,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Not good at drawing,no big deal
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:30.65,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Let me go for my one true belief
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:32.34,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Overcome myself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:32.34,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:Overcome yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:35.63,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:"A Ahole New World God Only Knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.50,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:I'll always be on your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:39.86,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:I know you're hurting inside
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:42.86,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:To be a knight D:To be a light L:For you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:43.70,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:We'll be shining bright
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:44.66,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:No more fears D:No more tears
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.81,0:01:46.02,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Everything will work out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.20,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  That's "God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:50.52,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Don't get me wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:52.82,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  This is not real love but
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:55.48,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:I'll do anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:58.69,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:Whatever happens in my life,turn the page and come of age
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:01.70,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Remember,no one can judge me
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.84,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}L:Every end leads to a new beginning of rhe next stage
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.55,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}E:Try to make my life complete,trust myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:07.01,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}D:Be strong and do my best
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:13.28,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Don't look back,carry on
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:14.89,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}C:Be yourself... Be happy... It's your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.14,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  "God only knows"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.71,JPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  Find your love... Find your way... For your life...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:31.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.93,0:00:55.87,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不願讓機會溜掉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.17,0:00:59.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  為什麼會被剝奪自由
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.91,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  與感性相對比的理性
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.06,0:01:06.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不得不克服失望感
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.83,0:01:10.08,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  所有努力決不會白費
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.23,0:01:13.04,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  就像沒有終點的慾望翻覆於心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.20,0:01:16.44,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  理想與現實之間的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:18.90,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  應該有改變時間的方法的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.05,0:01:20.42,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  對 就這麼交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.77,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不固定音程去唱歌 也沒什麼大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.99,0:01:25.85,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  糟糕的繪畫也無所謂 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.04,0:01:30.65,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我為了唯一的信念而前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:32.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我要勝過我自己  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:32.34,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  你要勝過你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.65,0:01:35.63,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  "只有神知道的全新世界"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:38.50,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我一直都是你的夥伴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.14,0:01:39.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我知道你在痛苦著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.51,0:01:42.86,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  成為騎士,成為照耀你的明燈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.90,0:01:43.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  我們會就這樣閃耀下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:44.66,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  已經不再恐懼 不再流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.81,0:01:46.02,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  一切都會順利的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.20,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  這便是"只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.43,0:01:50.52,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  別誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.70,0:01:52.82,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  這不是現實中的戀愛 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.99,0:01:55.48,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  為了你 我願意做任何事情
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:58.69,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  無論我的生命中發生什麼事 都會翻過嶄新的一頁長大成人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.34,0:02:01.70,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不要忘記 我不想被任何人所評說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.85,0:02:01.84,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  一切的終結都通往著下一個舞台的開始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:04.55,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  理解走過的人生 相信自己
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:07.01,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  變得更強 做到最好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.19,0:02:13.28,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  不回首過去 持續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:14.89,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  活出你自己的幸福... 因為這是你自己的人生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.10,0:02:16.14,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  "只有神知道"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.30,0:02:19.71,CHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(150,150)}  找到愛... 找到道路... 為了你自己的人生
